       MONITOR (computer monitor):
       <p>
        Draw a square in the air with your index fingertips.
        <p>
         <img border="0" height="266" src="/images/monito7.jpg" width="320"/>
         <img border="0" height="266" src="/images/monito8.jpg" width="320"/>
         <br/>
