         </iframe>
        </p>
        <hr align="left" color="#000000" size="1"/>
        <p>
         Note: If you do this sign "larger" it can mean "board" as in white board or 
	blackboard.
        </p>
        <p>
         “SQUARE-perimeter” can be used to indicate a billboard or display
  sign.  This is a very "general" sign used to indicate whatever
  is "square shaped."
         <br/>
         <br/>
         Add black to it and you have:  BLACK + BOARD
         <br/>
         Add White to it and you have:  WHITE + BOARD
        </p>
